               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18460706-name-486" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-486" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-486" type="surname" value="HORNBLOW"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-486" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE HORNBLOW</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in the habit of receiving newspapers from Mr. Ballantine—on the 26th of May I paid the prisoner 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for Mr. Ballantine, and have the receipt.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18460706-name-487" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-487" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
